{"tid":1385651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵係咪好似可以問佢拎返遲到證明？","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:38:44.000Z","uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af67743ded31ee6883cc44673da78917df21b401","tid":1385651,"uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"註：呢篇唔係撩交嗌文，我贊成抗爭要有犧牲的。<br />\n<br />\n今日同事同我呻佢老婆返工因為不合作運動而遲左兩小時返工，因而被某永X百貨扣糧半日，成為Collateral Damage<br />\n<br />\n想問之前好似有巴打提過係咪只要八達通有入閘證明，就可以問返地鐵因為佢地事估而拎返張證明書？雖然X安百貨就算有證明都未必會俾返半日人工佢，但都希望幫得就幫，我同事屋企手停口停。<br />\n<br />\n利申，我同事屋企住上環，星期日一家三口係屋企已經俾催淚彈燻到一屋都係，已經唔係第一次受波及。"},{"pid":"a1f8008a44dc61a1ee7d585f8373d13fe0749b16","tid":1385651,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"Fact checked<br />\n明天機場博覽館要人！！<br />\n7.31<br />\n16:00-17:30<br />\n機場Asia World Expo-Summit 2號展館<br />\n政府開pre policy address meeting! <br />\n會議是為運輸及貿易界而設既諮詢會，將有好多公司出席！<br />\n<br />\n聽日7.31機場博覽館要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35c595807b6fa99bdaeb1e189196c758949820be","tid":1385651,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46ca67254510d055b03c91d748cda452fa10e84a","tid":1385651,"uid":284676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"可以!!! 問客服拎就可以"},{"pid":"e01d18695d2bbfe99c8117df97b1de8024609743","tid":1385651,"uid":11770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"港鐵公司就早前觀塘綫受阻的情況，所發之延遲證明書<br />\n<br />\nDelay certificate issued by #MTR for disruptions on Kwun Tong Line<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tnsms1.mtr.com.hk/latecert/form_en.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftnsms1.mtr.com.hk%2Flatecert%2Fform_en.php&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=6d9667f2\" tar